<item>
            <title>[CXF-7585] base64 attachment encoding does not close the InputSteam</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-7585</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;AttachmentSerializer&lt;/tt&gt; class gets in the &lt;tt&gt;writeAttachments()&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;InputStream&lt;/tt&gt; from the &lt;tt&gt;DataHandler&lt;/tt&gt; and calls the &lt;tt&gt;encodeBase64(..)&lt;/tt&gt; method.&lt;br/&gt;
However, it does not close the InputStream.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead a try-with-resource approach should be used here&lt;/p&gt;</description>
